{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01YPzUnNtCNexkyZ75tgS9C1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Ralph Fix Plan\n2\t\n3\t## CRITICAL: Packages Need Installing\n4\tRun this command before testing: `pnpm install`\n5\t\n6\t## High Priority\n7\t- [x] Submitting destination + date range + guests returns only hotels matching `destination` and where `maxGuests >= guests`.\n8\t- [x] Leaving all fields empty returns the full hotel list.\n9\t- [x] Loading state shown while results are fetched.\n10\t- [x] Empty state shown when zero hotels match, with a \"reset filters\" action.\n11\t- [ ] Error state shown with retry if `/api/hotels` fails.\n12\t- [x] Setting min/max price filters out hotels outside that range.\n13\t- [x] Setting a minimum star rating filters out hotels below it.\n14\t- [x] Selecting amenities filters to hotels containing all selected amenities.\n15\t- [x] Sort control reorders results by price (asc/desc) or rating (desc) without a full page reload.\n16\t- [x] Details page renders name, address, star rating, description, amenities, and photo gallery for a valid `:id`.\n17\t- [x] Requesting an invalid/nonexistent `:id` shows a not-found state, not a crash.\n18\t- [x] Price breakdown reflects current date range and guest count.\n19\t- [ ] Results page shows a map with a pin per visible result; clicking a pin highlights/scrolls to the matching card.\n20\t- [ ] Hotel details page shows a single-pin map at the hotel's location.\n21\t- [ ] Map failing to load does not block viewing the list/details content.\n22\t- [x] Hotel details page lists all reviews for that hotel with guest name, rating, text, and date.\n23\t- [x] Hotel with zero reviews shows an empty state, not a broken list.\n24\t- [x] Submitting a review with name, rating (1-5), and text creates it via `POST /api/hotels/:id/reviews` and it appears in the list without a full page reload.\n25\t- [x] Submitting with a missing required field is blocked client-side with a visible validation message.\n26\t- [x] Submitted review updates the hotel's `averageRating`/`reviewCount`.\n27\t- [x] Clicking the heart on any hotel card toggles favorited state immediately (optimistic).\n28\t- [x] Favorited state persists across page reloads via `localStorage`.\n29\t- [x] Favorite state is consistent between the results list and the details page for the same hotel.\n30\t- [x] Favorites page lists all hotels currently saved in `localStorage`.\n31\t- [x] Favorites page shows an empty state with a link back to search when none are saved.\n32\t- [x] Unfavoriting from the favorites page removes it from the grid immediately.\n33\t- [x] Changing check-in/check-out dates or guest count on the details page recalculates and displays nights × rate = total.\n34\t- [x] Guest count exceeding `maxGuests` is blocked with an inline message.\n35\t- [x] Invalid date range (checkout before/equal to checkin) is blocked with an inline message.\n36\t- [x] Checkout form requires guest name, email, and mock payment fields before submission is enabled.\n37\t\n38\t\n39\t## Medium Priority\n40\t- [ ] Add map view (Leaflet + OpenStreetMap) to results and detail pages\n41\t- [ ] Error boundary / error state for API failures with retry\n42\t- [ ] CI pipeline (GitHub Actions workflow)\n43\t\n44\t\n45\t## Low Priority\n46\t- [ ] E2E test with Playwright (happy path)\n47\t- [ ] Toast notifications for favorites / review submitted\n48\t- [ ] README update with architecture notes, tradeoffs, LLM usage\n49\t\n50\t\n51\t## Completed\n52\t- [x] Project enabled for Ralph\n53\t- [x] Foundation: types, mock data, Zod schemas, data helpers (lib/hotels.ts, lib/bookings.ts)\n54\t- [x] All API route handlers (hotels list/detail/reviews/availability, bookings create/get)\n55\t- [x] Zustand favorites store with localStorage persistence\n56\t- [x] Components: HotelCard, SearchBar, FilterPanel, StarRating, PhotoGallery, AmenitiesList\n57\t- [x] Components: ReviewList, ReviewForm, DateGuestPicker, CheckoutForm\n58\t- [x] Components: FavoriteButton, EmptyState, ErrorState, LoadingSkeleton\n59\t- [x] Pages: Home (search/results), Hotel detail, Favorites, Checkout, Confirmation\n60\t- [x] not-found pages for hotel and booking\n61\t- [x] Unit tests: filter-hotels, pricing, schemas\n62\t- [x] Next.js image config for Unsplash\n63\t- [x] Vitest config and test setup\n64\t\n65\t## Notes\n66\t- Focus on MVP functionality first\n67\t- Ensure each feature is properly tested\n68\t- Update this file after each major milestone\n69\t- BLOCKER: pnpm install needs user approval — run `pnpm install` to unblock\n70\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1a46cfe3-edd5-47d3-88ea-9b5bc1fd0648","uuid":"a0578e17-3af5-43ac-a78c-4f9d40ea22ce","timestamp":"2026-07-02T15:21:19.832Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/rensknoors/repos/lateral-assessment/.ralph/fix_plan.md","content":"# Ralph Fix Plan\n\n## CRITICAL: Packages Need Installing\nRun this command before testing: `pnpm install`\n\n## High Priority\n- [x] Submitting destination + date range + guests returns only hotels matching `destination` and where `maxGuests >= guests`.\n- [x] Leaving all fields empty returns the full hotel list.\n- [x] Loading state shown while results are fetched.\n- [x] Empty state shown when zero hotels match, with a \"reset filters\" action.\n- [ ] Error state shown with retry if `/api/hotels` fails.\n- [x] Setting min/max price filters out hotels outside that range.\n- [x] Setting a minimum star rating filters out hotels below it.\n- [x] Selecting amenities filters to hotels containing all selected amenities.\n- [x] Sort control reorders results by price (asc/desc) or rating (desc) without a full page reload.\n- [x] Details page renders name, address, star rating, description, amenities, and photo gallery for a valid `:id`.\n- [x] Requesting an invalid/nonexistent `:id` shows a not-found state, not a crash.\n- [x] Price breakdown reflects current date range and guest